John R. POLGAR, Jr., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Theresa DEES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D16-4027 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 14, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellee's motion to dismiss is granted, and this appeal is dismissed for failing to comply with this court's April 24, 2018, order. Appellant's motion for an extension of time to serve the initial brief is denied as moot. Appellant's motion to withdraw objection is denied as moot.

VILLANTI, SLEET, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUKIM, JJ., Concur.
